              <p>Along these lines, something like psql’s expanded display (<a href="https://coderwall.com/p/rftixq/postgres-expanded-display" rel="nofollow noopener">example</a>) would be a great option to be able to set a table to use.</p>
<p>Particularly helps where you have a few rows but many columns.</p>
