              <p>I was planning on implementing something like the Postgres extended display as an example of a new visualization, but your idea of a text block widget associated with a query is also a good one!</p>
<p>I will update here if I get to this any time soon.</p>
<p>Of course, PRs are welcomed <img src="https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=9" title=":slight_smile:" class="emoji" alt=":slight_smile:"> Note that new visualizations should be implemented with React.</p>
